{"tid":1325600,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷到琴晚都仲講緊佢阻人衝立法會好威，證明佢根本無企過係義士一邊","createTime":"2019-07-17T02:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T09:27:07.000Z","uid":63364,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3db9590a9e1f83f7ba1d5611ce300ef166f239c2","tid":1325600,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:32:58.000Z","msg":"不分化，但唔屌唔得<br />\n雖然我都唔覺得昨晚新城市要勇武<br />\n不過林卓廷同莊榮輝呢兩條撚樣<br />\n我屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n又影鳩人相<br />\n又篤灰<br />\n又最人去圍新鴻基總部<br />\n吖唔係，係叫人去新鴻基總部抗議<br />\n唔知以為佢老細係新鴻基<br />\n<br />\n又話唔認同衝立法會<br />\n我屌你老母啦<br />\n佔領立法會嘅政治意義你到今日都未理解到<br />\n食屎啦林卓廷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係咪衝完立法會阻鳩住你地通過警察加薪啊！<br />\n講到尾咪又係為選票<br />\n莊榮輝抵選極都選唔到</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f1984c754579fc0db74049e097d5232d8a7908bd","tid":1325600,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00e3479c549f356018f152e1ff78a7478844c0dd","tid":1325600,"uid":93241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"佢日日都係上水條橋到播今天我  做咁耐區議無搞過水貨"},{"pid":"edfd35f1e22652f6f643ca70adc0262838442e0c","tid":1325600,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9682c952186b09384f1216c12827a6211a456aaa","tid":1325600,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00e3479c549f356018f152e1ff78a7478844c0dd","tid":1325600,"uid":93241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"佢日日都係上水條橋到播今天我  做咁耐區議無搞過水貨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"上水佢地頭<br />\n我屌佢老母"},{"pid":"cc7722e80d86eef193b0a87cdc7fe8644e3da80d","tid":1325600,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b580d6e4d6894356b7c8ee23898c4bf118ef1ca6","tid":1325600,"uid":93241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9682c952186b09384f1216c12827a6211a456aaa","tid":1325600,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00e3479c549f356018f152e1ff78a7478844c0dd","tid":1325600,"uid":93241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"佢日日都係上水條橋到播今天我  做咁耐區議無搞過水貨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"上水佢地頭<br />\n我屌佢老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"自己區內野 都未做好過"},{"pid":"475448d3f7d4196032a56ed0b5b045b9eb778cb3","tid":1325600,"uid":10466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"下次佢再係咁就抬佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71c83af5e7f2227519534fae28dadeeb012e7db","tid":1325600,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實好多泛民民主黨仲係好唔認同衝立法會，認為有鬼<br />\n<br />\n當初真係好危險，好彩連登仔接連化險為夷<br />\n首先成功衝入去，半途而廢實被班勝利球迷屌鬼<br />\n其次係初期雖然有破壞既衝動，但連登仔理性聲音成功傳到示威者到叫讀聲明，作出政治宣言扭轉整個形勢，將破壞轉化成政治表態<br />\n<br />\n就係靠呢兩點用局勢鎮住班屌鬼飯民，佢哋先唔敢大聲屌，但你永遠改變唔到佢哋觀感，要記住而家只係喺不分化前題下有限度合作既同路人，局勢一轉就講bye bye"},{"pid":"0785b443f2a29e41347cb1ffe2fccbd8de729e2f","tid":1325600,"uid":281763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"林博出位博得好明顯"},{"pid":"214504d228cdfb136c099c8095f469b7f15ec7f8","tid":1325600,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:22:20.000Z","msg":"-文宣-聯署-民意授權-721警員射波大聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1326199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1326199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"14c6fed28f22a12aa406d1a851fbecc8a56e9d81","tid":1325600,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"泛民好多人<br />\n仲有個思想<br />\n覺得呢啲活動仲可以有大台<br />\n有人可以企出黎做指揮"},{"pid":"ca4c1ebd38ab39f642ead886fd5c18f7f6f1bee5","tid":1325600,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"